    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >选秀节目现场中发生的的命案谜团。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过“交流 × 生存 × 冒险”揭开隐藏的真相。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1025960/extras/f114058466268685a479535bbb3cb880.avif?t=1747276302\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1025960/extras_big/f114058466268685a479535bbb3cb880.avif?t=1747276302 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《深埋之星》由韩国人气冒险游戏《黑房》和《灰色都市》的开发团队 Studio LARGO 与 LINE Games 联合打造，呈现的悬疑冒险游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>选秀节目直播现场突发坍塌事故与凶案</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1025960/extras/93f2d6f95d7717978d069ca5f5b30500.poster.avif?t=1747276302\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1025960/extras/93f2d6f95d7717978d069ca5f5b30500.webm?t=1747276302\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1025960/extras/93f2d6f95d7717978d069ca5f5b30500.mp4?t=1747276302\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在一档普通的素人生存选秀节目直播中，演播厅突然坍塌，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >被困其中的参赛者和工作人员却又陷入了更可怕的谋杀事件。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >凶手究竟是谁？为何而来？如何作案？</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>3D 场景 × 2D 角色的戏剧化演出</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >将美术风格鲜明的 2D 角色融入 3D 崩塌环境之中，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >展现出富有张力、沉浸感十足的视觉体验。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>沉浸式社交媒体玩法</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1025960/extras/784a73de5df18831f72333359b4929b2.avif?t=1747276302\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1025960/extras_big/784a73de5df18831f72333359b4929b2.avif?t=1747276302 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过游戏内的“社交媒体”与“时间线”系统，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可深感角色的情况和环境，同时也可以获取解谜的关键线索。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>分支剧情与多个结局</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1025960/extras/bc7660e23580949bd6343e91fb3b9799.avif?t=1747276302\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1025960/extras_big/bc7660e23580949bd6343e91fb3b9799.avif?t=1747276302 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的每一个选择都会影响故事的走向。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过对话、选择与多周目探索，逐步揭示所有角色的真相与结局。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>原声音乐与沉浸式音效设计</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1025960/extras/dffc14a8c4ffde00de903c1d4d87cc05.poster.avif?t=1747276302\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1025960/extras/dffc14a8c4ffde00de903c1d4d87cc05.webm?t=1747276302\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1025960/extras/dffc14a8c4ffde00de903c1d4d87cc05.mp4?t=1747276302\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >包括主题曲《Be Honest》在内的各种原创音乐、背景音乐与效果组成的音响设计，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >让您逐渐走入到故事之中。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>豪华日韩声优全语音演出</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1025960/extras/bda8e2667f7ed4ba0752855e32777530.poster.avif?t=1747276302\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1025960/extras/bda8e2667f7ed4ba0752855e32777530.webm?t=1747276302\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1025960/extras/bda8e2667f7ed4ba0752855e32777530.mp4?t=1747276302\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >韩语与日语配音版本皆由一线声优倾情献声，带来深度沉浸的剧情演出。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>日语配音</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >KAKIHARA Tetsuya、EGUCHI Takuya、SHIMONO Hiro、HIKASA Yoko、SATO Rina、HOSHI Soichiro、KITAMURA Eri等</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>韩语配音</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >PARK Sung-tae、RYU Seung-gon、NAM Do-hyung、KIM Yeon-woo、KIM Ha-ru、LEE Kyung-tae、IM Yoon-seon等</p>",
